KEYBINDINGS
===========

Mode Independent / Mode Change
------------------------------

`   = Switch to Movement Mode
l   = Look around
@   = Character Screen
i   = Inventory Screen
?   = Game Info
F1  = Help text (Not implemented)
F12 = Quit

Movement Mode
-------------

qwe 789
asd 456 = Movement
zxc 123

Arrow Keys = Move Camera
<  = Go up stairs
>  = Go down stairs

, = Pickup gold/items
p = Drink a potion

Map Look Mode
-------------

qwe 789
asd 456 = Move reticle
zxc 123

Arrow Keys = Move Camera






ITEMS
=====

Potions
-------

Potions come in varying potencies and varying effects. Potencies are, from least
to most,

    Minor,
    Lesser,
    Light,
    Moderate,
    Average,
    Strong

Effects are

    Healing         --  Recovers HP
    Enervation      --  Recovers MP
    Rejuvenation    --  Recovers both
